x_1,x_2,x_3,\dotsc,x_n
\frac{1}{2}
\frac{1-x_1}{1+x_1}\cdot\frac{1-x_2}{1+x_2}\cdot\frac{1-x_3}{1+x_3}\cdots\frac{1-x_n}{1+x_n}\geq\frac{1}{3}.
\prod_{i=1}^{n}(1-x_i)>1-\sum_{i=1}^{n}(x_i)=1-\frac12=\frac12.
\prod_{i=1}^{n}(1+x_i)<\frac32.
\prod_{i=1}^{n}(1+x_i)>1+\sum_{i=1}^{n}(x_i)=\frac32.
