x_j
x_i
x_j = x
x_i = \frac{1}{2} - x
\frac{(1 - x)(\frac{1}{2} +x)}{(1+ x)(\frac{3}{2} - x)} = \frac{\frac{1}{2} + x(\frac{1}{2} - x)}{\frac{3}{2} + x(\frac{1}{2} - x)} \ge \frac{\frac{1}{2}}{\frac{3}{2}} =  \frac{1}{3}
